{"tid":1267344,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】21歲大學生留「反送中」字句墮斃 教大將辦悼念儀式","createTime":"2019-06-29T21:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T01:00:25.000Z","uid":224338,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b2e433c1449ebcf5990426ce384c5a937dc1a1","tid":1267344,"uid":224338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T21:34:47.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，一名21歲女子由粉嶺嘉福邨福泰樓的高處墮下，頭爆肢折倒卧地上，救援人員到場證實她傷重不治。事後一名女親友事後到場認屍，其間有人激動痛哭，場面哀傷。<br />\n<br />\n據知，女死者姓盧，與家人住在上水，並非上址住客，她去年入讀教育大學創意藝術與文化（音樂）系，大約2至3星期前開始拍拖，惟至近日雙方發生爭執冷戰。消息指，女死者早前曾多次參與遊行及集會，但未有通宵留守，她今日疑在墮樓前，曾用紅筆在24樓的梯間牆壁上寫有「反送中」及近一百字的文章，內容提及「雖然抗爭時間久了，但絕對不能忘記，我們一直以來的理念，一定要堅持下去，強烈要求全面撤回條例，收回暴動論，釋放學生示威者&hellip;本人願可以小命成功換取二百萬人的心願，請你們堅持下去」，然後將相片上載至ig。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59771130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59771130&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=9216ab8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59771130&h=852cd083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59771130</a>"},{"pid":"2affdd26f4eb8a52f453ff140118c9510974cf7d","tid":1267344,"uid":225247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T23:30:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d91d6e196c2eb11e814cc674a25f6b5ab538ac7","tid":1267344,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T23:33:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母又係假新聞"},{"pid":"9116ea009c99bbce52ab9ec45f3368bd1a494627","tid":1267344,"uid":256014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:00:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　　２９號</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">３０號</span><span style=\"color: red;\">各</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一個，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">合共</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">３個，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">夠了，</span>不要再多，<span style=\"color: brown;\">因為</span><span style=\"color: red;\">到</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">這一刻，</span><span style=\"color: green;\">我</span>不覺得<span style=\"color: green;\">林鄭月娥</span>條死八婆<span style=\"color: brown;\">會</span><span style=\"color: red;\">關注</span>這類死者。</strong></span>"}]}